\lim_{x\rightarrow\infty}\left[1+\frac{a}{x}\right]^x=\operatorname{exp}[a]
x
a
f(x,a)
\left|\left[1+\frac{a}{x}\right]^x-\operatorname{exp}[a]\right|=\mathcal{O}(f(x,a))
x\gg a
\left(1+\frac{a}{x}\right)^x=\exp\left(x\ln\left(1+\frac{a}{x}\right)\right).
\left(1+\frac{a}{x}\right)^x\approx\exp\left(x\left[\frac{a}{x}-\frac{a^2}{2x^2}\right]\right)=e^a\cdot e^{-a^2/2x}\approx e^a\left(1-\frac{a^2}{2x}\right).
f(x,a)=\frac{a^2 e^a}{2x}.
